exact_source: CuFe Ltd (ASX: CUF) (CuFe or the Company) is pleased to announce that all conditions precedent to the sale of the Company’s Mining Rights at JWD to Newcam Minerals Pty Ltd (Newcam) (as announced to ASX on 26 August 2024) were met by 31 October 2024 and that settlement of the transaction completed on 1 November 2024.
